name: Juicebox Events
description:
Going above and beyond the norm to create memorable experiences and bring visions to life for Juicebox DAO. 

From Ice Cream Socials and hack-a-thons to project creation workshops and good ol' irl hang sessions, we're here for it. 

Funds will be used to for the planning and execution of events. 

Visit JB discord to learn about current events in the works!
